{% comment %}
  VELLOR Ambassador Page
  Application form + benefits for brand ambassadors
{% endcomment %}

<section id="ambassador-{{ section.id }}" class="vellor-ambassador">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <div class="vellor-ambassador__hero">
    <h1 class="vellor-ambassador__title">Represent VELLOR</h1>
    <p class="vellor-ambassador__subtitle">We're looking for people who live in what they wear. Not influencers. Not models. Just real ones.</p>
  </div>

  <!-- What You Get -->
  <div class="vellor-ambassador__benefits">
    <div class="vellor-ambassador__benefits-inner">
      <p class="vellor-ambassador__label">What You Get</p>
      <div class="vellor-ambassador__benefits-grid">
        <div class="vellor-ambassador__benefit">
          <h3 class="vellor-ambassador__benefit-title">Free Product</h3>
          <p class="vellor-ambassador__benefit-text">Receive pieces from every drop before anyone else. Wear it, live in it, share it.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="vellor-ambassador__benefit">
          <h3 class="vellor-ambassador__benefit-title">Commission</h3>
          <p class="vellor-ambassador__benefit-text">Earn on every sale through your personal link. The more you share, the more you make.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="vellor-ambassador__benefit">
          <h3 class="vellor-ambassador__benefit-title">Early Access</h3>
          <p class="vellor-ambassador__benefit-text">See new collections before they launch. Be the first to wear what's next.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="vellor-ambassador__benefit">
          <h3 class="vellor-ambassador__benefit-title">Community</h3>
          <p class="vellor-ambassador__benefit-text">Join a crew of people building something. Private group, direct access, real connection.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- What You'll Create -->
  <div class="vellor-ambassador__create">
    <div class="vellor-ambassador__create-inner">
      <p class="vellor-ambassador__label">What You'll Create</p>
      <h2 class="vellor-ambassador__who-heading">Content that stops the scroll.</h2>
      <div class="vellor-ambassador__who-text" style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
        <p>We don't want polished ads. We want real content from real people wearing VELLOR in real life. The kind of content that makes someone stop scrolling because it feels authentic — not because it looks like a commercial.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="vellor-ambassador__benefits-grid">
        <div class="vellor-ambassador__benefit">
          <h3 class="vellor-ambassador__benefit-title">Get Ready With Me</h3>
          <p class="vellor-ambassador__benefit-text">Film yourself getting dressed. Show the texture, the fit, how it moves. Talk about why you reach for it. Keep it real — that's what works.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="vellor-ambassador__benefit">
          <h3 class="vellor-ambassador__benefit-title">Day-in-the-Life</h3>
          <p class="vellor-ambassador__benefit-text">Wear VELLOR through your actual day. Gym, coffee, errands, work. Don't stage it. Just live in it and let the camera catch what it catches.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="vellor-ambassador__benefit">
          <h3 class="vellor-ambassador__benefit-title">Unboxing + First Impressions</h3>
          <p class="vellor-ambassador__benefit-text">Open the package on camera. React to the weight of the fleece, the V embroidery, the color. First impressions hit different when they're genuine.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="vellor-ambassador__benefit">
          <h3 class="vellor-ambassador__benefit-title">Style Comparisons</h3>
          <p class="vellor-ambassador__benefit-text">Show VELLOR next to what you normally wear. Side by side. Let people see the difference in quality, fit, and feel without you having to say it.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Tiers -->
  <div class="vellor-ambassador__who">
    <div class="vellor-ambassador__who-inner">
      <p class="vellor-ambassador__label" style="color: rgba(242,242,242,0.2);">Ambassador Tiers</p>
      <h2 class="vellor-ambassador__who-heading">Start where you are. Level up as you grow.</h2>
      <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 1.5rem; margin-top: 2rem;">
        <div style="padding: 1.5rem; border: 1px solid rgba(242,242,242,0.08); border-radius: 12px;">
          <h3 style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 1.2rem; color: #F2F2F2; margin: 0 0 0.5rem;">Tier 1 — Starter</h3>
          <p style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: #999; line-height: 1.7; margin: 0;">0-5K followers. You get free product + a personal discount code. Post 2x/month minimum. We use your content in our ads (with credit). You earn 10% commission on every sale from your code.</p>
        </div>
        <div style="padding: 1.5rem; border: 1px solid rgba(242,242,242,0.08); border-radius: 12px;">
          <h3 style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 1.2rem; color: #F2F2F2; margin: 0 0 0.5rem;">Tier 2 — Core</h3>
          <p style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: #999; line-height: 1.7; margin: 0;">5K-50K followers. Everything in Tier 1 plus: monthly content briefs, priority access to new drops, featured on our website and social, 15% commission, and a monthly stipend for top performers.</p>
        </div>
        <div style="padding: 1.5rem; border: 1px solid rgba(242,242,242,0.08); border-radius: 12px;">
          <h3 style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 1.2rem; color: #F2F2F2; margin: 0 0 0.5rem;">Tier 3 — Partner</h3>
          <p style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: #999; line-height: 1.7; margin: 0;">50K+ followers or proven sales performance. Custom collaboration deals, co-designed product opportunities, paid campaign work, 20% commission, and direct line to the team.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Application Form -->
  <div class="vellor-ambassador__form-section">
    <div class="vellor-ambassador__form-inner">
      <p class="vellor-ambassador__label">Apply</p>
      <h2 class="vellor-ambassador__form-heading">Tell us about yourself.</h2>

      <form class="vellor-ambassador__form" id="ambassador-form">
        <div class="vellor-ambassador__form-grid">
          <div class="vellor-ambassador__field">
            <label class="vellor-ambassador__field-label">First Name</label>
            <input type="text" name="first_name" required class="vellor-ambassador__input" placeholder="First name">
          </div>
          <div class="vellor-ambassador__field">
            <label class="vellor-ambassador__field-label">Last Name</label>
            <input type="text" name="last_name" required class="vellor-ambassador__input" placeholder="Last name">
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="vellor-ambassador__field">
          <label class="vellor-ambassador__field-label">Email</label>
          <input type="email" name="email" required class="vellor-ambassador__input" placeholder="Email address">
        </div>

        <div class="vellor-ambassador__field">
          <label class="vellor-ambassador__field-label">Instagram Handle</label>
          <input type="text" name="instagram" class="vellor-ambassador__input" placeholder="@yourhandle">
        </div>

        <div class="vellor-ambassador__field">
          <label class="vellor-ambassador__field-label">TikTok Handle</label>
          <input type="text" name="tiktok" class="vellor-ambassador__input" placeholder="@yourhandle">
        </div>

        <div class="vellor-ambassador__field">
          <label class="vellor-ambassador__field-label">Why VELLOR?</label>
          <textarea name="why" rows="4" class="vellor-ambassador__textarea" placeholder="What draws you to the brand? What are you building?"></textarea>
        </div>

        <div class="vellor-ambassador__field">
          <label class="vellor-ambassador__field-label">Your Size</label>
          <div class="vellor-ambassador__size-options">
            {% for size in "XS,S,M,L,XL" | split: "," %}
              <label class="vellor-ambassador__size-label">
                <input type="radio" name="size" value="{{ size }}" class="vellor-ambassador__size-radio">
                <span class="vellor-ambassador__size-btn">{{ size }}</span>
              </label>
            {% endfor %}
          </div>
        </div>

        <button type="submit" class="vellor-ambassador__submit" id="ambassador-submit">
          Submit Application
        </button>

        <p class="vellor-ambassador__form-note">We review every application. If we think it's a fit, we'll reach out within 7 days.</p>
      </form>

      <div class="vellor-ambassador__success" id="ambassador-success" style="display: none;">
        <h3 class="vellor-ambassador__success-heading">Application received.</h3>
        <p class="vellor-ambassador__success-text">We'll review your application and get back to you within 7 days if it's a fit. Keep building.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</section>

<script>
  (function() {
    var form = document.getElementById('ambassador-form');
    var successEl = document.getElementById('ambassador-success');
    var submitBtn = document.getElementById('ambassador-submit');

    if (!form) return;

    form.addEventListener('submit', function(e) {
      e.preventDefault();

      submitBtn.disabled = true;
      submitBtn.textContent = 'Submitting...';

      var formData = new FormData(form);
      var data = {};
      formData.forEach(function(value, key) { data[key] = value; });

      /* Send to GHL webhook or Shopify customer */
      fetch('/contact', {
        method: 'POST',
        headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/x-www-form-urlencoded' },
        body: new URLSearchParams({
          'form_type': 'customer',
          'utf8': '\u2713',
          'contact[email]': data.email,
          'contact[first_name]': data.first_name || '',
          'contact[last_name]': data.last_name || '',
          'contact[tags]': 'ambassador-applicant',
          'contact[note]': 'Ambassador Application\nInstagram: ' + (data.instagram || 'N/A') + '\nTikTok: ' + (data.tiktok || 'N/A') + '\nSize: ' + (data.size || 'N/A') + '\nWhy: ' + (data.why || 'N/A')
        }).toString()
      })
      .then(function() {
        form.style.display = 'none';
        successEl.style.display = 'block';
      })
      .catch(function() {
        form.style.display = 'none';
        successEl.style.display = 'block';
      });
    });
  })();
</script>

<style>
  #ambassador-{{ section.id }} {
    color: #1C1C1C;
  }

  .vellor-ambassador__hero {
    background-color: #0A0A0A;
    padding: 8rem 2rem 5rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .vellor-ambassador__title {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 5rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    color: #F2F2F2;
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .vellor-ambassador__subtitle {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: rgba(242,242,242,0.4);
    max-width: 500px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .vellor-ambassador__label {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.25em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #999;
    margin: 0 0 2rem;
  }

  /* Benefits */
  .vellor-ambassador__benefits {
    background: #F2F2F2;
    padding: 5rem 2rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 769px) {
    .vellor-ambassador__benefits { padding: 7rem 3rem; }
  }

  .vellor-ambassador__benefits-inner {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .vellor-ambassador__benefits-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 2.5rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 769px) {
    .vellor-ambassador__benefits-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 3rem;
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .vellor-ambassador__benefits-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    }
  }

  .vellor-ambassador__benefit-title {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
    color: #1C1C1C;
  }

  .vellor-ambassador__benefit-text {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #999;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* Who */
  .vellor-ambassador__who {
    background: #0A0A0A;
    padding: 5rem 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  @media (min-width: 769px) {
    .vellor-ambassador__who { padding: 7rem 3rem; }
  }

  .vellor-ambassador__who-inner {
    max-width: 650px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .vellor-ambassador__who .vellor-ambassador__label {
    color: rgba(242,242,242,0.2);
  }

  .vellor-ambassador__who-heading {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.5rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    color: #F2F2F2;
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .vellor-ambassador__who-text {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: rgba(242,242,242,0.35);
  }

  .vellor-ambassador__who-text p { margin: 0; }

  /* Form */
  .vellor-ambassador__form-section {
    background: #F2F2F2;
    padding: 5rem 2rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 769px) {
    .vellor-ambassador__form-section { padding: 7rem 3rem; }
  }

  .vellor-ambassador__form-inner {
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .vellor-ambassador__form-heading {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.2rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    margin: 0 0 2.5rem;
    color: #1C1C1C;
  }

  .vellor-ambassador__form-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .vellor-ambassador__field {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .vellor-ambassador__field-label {
    display: block;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #999;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .vellor-ambassador__input,
  .vellor-ambassador__textarea {
    width: 100%;
    background: transparent;
    border: none;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    padding: 0.75rem 0;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: #1C1C1C;
    outline: none;
    transition: border-color 0.3s;
  }

  .vellor-ambassador__input:focus,
  .vellor-ambassador__textarea:focus {
    border-bottom-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
  }

  .vellor-ambassador__input::placeholder,
  .vellor-ambassador__textarea::placeholder {
    color: #ccc;
  }

  .vellor-ambassador__textarea {
    resize: none;
  }

  .vellor-ambassador__size-options {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  .vellor-ambassador__size-radio {
    display: none;
  }

  .vellor-ambassador__size-btn {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    color: #999;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }

  .vellor-ambassador__size-radio:checked + .vellor-ambassador__size-btn {
    background: #1C1C1C;
    color: #F2F2F2;
    border-color: #1C1C1C;
  }

  .vellor-ambassador__submit {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    background: #1C1C1C;
    color: #F2F2F2;
    border: none;
    padding: 1rem;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background 0.3s;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .vellor-ambassador__submit:hover {
    background: #333;
  }

  .vellor-ambassador__submit:disabled {
    opacity: 0.5;
    cursor: not-allowed;
  }

  .vellor-ambassador__form-note {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: #bbb;
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .vellor-ambassador__success-heading {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: #1C1C1C;
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
  }

  .vellor-ambassador__success-text {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: #999;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }
</style>

